ZH: 群众是社会的基础性质。
EN: The masses are the foundation of society.

ZH: 政府需要听取群众的意见。
EN: The government needs to listen to the opinions of the masses.

ZH: 群众的力量是巨大的。
EN: The power of the masses is enormous.

ZH: 社会主义的核心是为群众服务。
EN: The core of socialism is serving the masses.

ZH: 群众是国家的根基。
EN: The masses are the foundation of the country.

ZH: 群众是社会发展的推动力。
EN: The masses are the driving force of social development.

ZH: 勤劳的工人是群众的重要组成部分。
EN: Hard-working workers are an important part of the masses.

ZH: 群众是历史的主角。
EN: The masses are the protagonists of history.

ZH: 我们要紧紧依靠群众。
EN: We must rely closely on the masses.

ZH: 群众的利益需要得到保护。
EN: The interests of the masses need to be protected.

ZH: 群众的智慧是无穷的。
EN: The wisdom of the masses is boundless.

ZH: 团结一心，众人皆为群众。
EN: United we stand, all are part of the masses.

ZH: 群众的声音应该被听见。
EN: The voice of the masses should be heard.

ZH: 任何政策都要以群众的意愿为重。
EN: Any policy should prioritize the will of the masses.

ZH: 群众是历史进步的动力。
EN: The masses are the driving force of historical progress.

ZH: 人民的群众基础是我们的力量。
EN: The people's mass foundation is our strength.

ZH: 群众是社会的主体。
EN: The masses are the main body of society.

ZH: 必须保证群众的利益受到维护。
EN: It is necessary to ensure the interests of the masses are protected.

ZH: 群众需要接受正确的引导。
EN: The masses need to receive correct guidance.

ZH: 我们要深入基层，了解群众的真实需求。
EN: We need to go deep into the grassroots to understand the real needs of the masses.
